OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out near Kosher
OL,4,Csupermarket in Golders Green
OL,6,FA huge fire has broken out near a
OL,7,FKosher supermarket in Golders Green,
OL,8,Fnorth London.
OL,10,FThe fire was first reported at around
OL,11,F6.47am on Wednesday, with the London
OL,12,FFire Brigade (LFB) saying it had
OL,13,Freceived at least 56 calls.
OL,15,FIt appears to have started behind the
OL,16,FJewish supermarket Kosher Kingdom. The
OL,17,Fcause of the blaze is unknown at this
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
