OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779887471
OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out near Kosher
OL,4,Csupermarket in Golders Green
OL,6,FIn a statement, the LFB said: "The
OL,7,Ffire has occurred by a building which
OL,8,Fis three storeys, with a shop on the
OL,9,Fground floor and premises above.
OL,11,F"The fire is producing a significant
OL,12,Famount of smoke and we're advising
OL,13,Fpeople in the area to keep their
OL,14,Fwindows and doors shut at this time.
OL,16,F"Please avoid the area whilst
OL,17,Ffirefighters work to extinguish the
OL,18,Ffire."
