OL,3,CHuge fire breaks out near Kosher
OL,4,Csupermarket in Golders Green
OL,6,FAround ten fire engines and 70
OL,7,Ffirefighters from surrounding areas,
OL,8,Fincluding Finchley, Willesden and West
OL,9,FHampstead, were dispatched, the
OL,10,Fbrigade added.
OL,12,FA number of road closures are in
OL,13,Fplace, including on Golders Green Road
OL,14,Fnear the junction with Beverley
OL,15,FGardens.
